snippet.title: Mavericks Proving Grounds trailer - PC Gaming Show 2018
snippet.description:
One of our first proper looks at the massive, 400-player battle royale game. See more on http://www.pcgamer.com and watch the PC Gaming Show livestream at https://www.pcgamer.com/pc-gaming-show-2018-watch/

More on Proving Grounds here: https://mavericks.gg/
